snippet.title: Chin Wags | KJ has gone too far! Request for #woacb blackout! #katiejoy is harmful - use timestamps
snippet.description:
Cactus Bill request a full community blackout! Katie Joy aka woacb is sharing details from Josh Duggars trial, that could possibly jeopardise the trial. The case could be dropped, due to public prosecution. I'm appalled at kj's coverage, she is causing way more harm than she is even aware of. This is why the code of ethics exists and Katie is going against everything, set in place to protect the victims and the public from being further traumatised! I call for a woacb black out. 

Music: I can't think
Musician: Lost in the moment 
Music: Sycamore
Musician: Philip E Morris
BILL'S TIP JAR: paypal.me/itscrystalbill
*Chin Wags is Aussie slang for talking, chatting (:

2:08 My opinions are heavily formed from my past work for child protection & being a CSA survivor myself. 
2:49 DD - don't say/type the full title 
Don't share Katie's videos, don't be a part of the further distribution of these details! Don't let your curiosity to see or your need to make a video about it, distract from how damaging kjs words are to this CSA case! 
3:25 Katie could jeopardise this case! 
4:12 When kj first detailed Josh's csam downloads... First time I saw absolute evil in her eyes 
6:23 I've personally witnessed a CSA case that was dropped due to online public prosecution & it fkd me up for a long time afterwards. I can't stress this enough, please! Don't share her videos or posts about this trial, I'm begging you. 
7:45 Katie has shared info in her ig posts that name the Tor site used & I can assure you, her followers would have googled it, some will try find the files she is talking about, some will be horrifically affected by these details that they will need psychological help. This is the big picture of the harm kj is causing. 
9:15 Katie's IG post that set me off, I shared it on twitter but I won't be reading out the CSA she details. 
10:17 KJ has no trigger warnings, she wants to hurt her viewers imo she wants them traumatised, Katie doesn't care, again these are abuser traits. Abusers will never understand a victims pain & suffering, because they find delight in the details & even more delight in harming their audience, imo. 
11:40  it's not just kj, some of her followers also don't understand the magnitude of sensitive info being discussed. 
12:40 What kind of Journalist doesn't use trigger warnings? Imho, a predator or abuser. Everyone else CARES! 
13:30 Katie's reply to being asked to put a trigger warning on her posts... 
15:44 A lot of Katie's followers are from the special needs groups & / have special needs, these people are already vulnerable & the unnecessary details are going to affect her audience on a grand scale, imo. 
17:40 The Journalistic code of ethics, chapter on Minimising Harm! #katiejoy did you miss this section when you were building your reputable career? 
- I said 'spiteful' instead of 'spiritual', in the last sentence, apologies for that. 
20:55 Amber Portwood is that you? Nope it's Katie 'lacking emotional intelligence' Paulson, forcing herself to show emotion, yet all we see is a desperate attempt & crocodile tears.. 
25:57 Calling for a community blackout, regarding kj's coverage of JD's trial. Katie gets a buzz from audiences reaction to her coverage. Don't give her that. Also, don't share her shit. Take a week off, stand with the victims, let's make sure that Katie doesn't jeopardise this case!!!
31:56 I even tagged instagram in my tweet.. I've reported all her ig posts & I'm not telling you to do this but you should consider reporting her posts if you feel she has crossed certain boundaries. Katie will never learn, if the platforms she posts on do not start holding her accountable! Ffs! 
32:52 Someone who enjoys the details of CSA, should not be covering a CSA trial! I know detectives that are scarred by details of CSA, no one wants to know these details, no one I have ever come across irl, working in child protection & tracking predators online, never have I come across anyone willing to verbalise CSA details to an audience who are the general public..real journalists have a responsibility to minimise harm

dm links to vids you'd like Bill to react to: Twitter or Instagram @itscrystalbill

JOIN 🌵The Cacti Contributors 🌵 https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC9e4I4yt6-uTrUJec4ccYyQ/join

"For every action, there is an equal and opposite reaction" - N̶e̶w̶t̶o̶n̶'̶s̶ ̶t̶h̶i̶r̶d̶ ̶l̶a̶w̶ ̶o̶f̶ ̶m̶o̶t̶i̶o̶n̶ YouTube commentary.
